---
title: Linguine Melanzane with blistered cherry tomatoes
description: Translated from Italian, melanzane is aubergine, a vegetable that's today integral to the country's cuisine. In this particular recipe, it's slow-roasted with sesame oil and paired with beautifully blistered cherry tomatoes to create a tempting veggie pasta dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R08_W24_IE_IEVV14271-3_Main_high-c441bd66.jpg
